|publisher=[[Johnston Press]]
|date=2009-05-22
|accessdate=2011-05-13}}</ref> ''[[The Guardian]]'' mentioned it in October 2010 as something Friday was "rumoured to have done".<ref name=roughley/> Roger Titford's December 2010 work, ''The Legend of Robin Friday'', categorically denied that it happened and claimed that the story had originated "on some punk football T-shirt website".<ref name="Titford46">{{cite book
| last=Titford
| page=46
| year=2010}}</ref>
